{"tid":607242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫隻鸚鵡打格仔係咩玩法","createTime":"2018-03-27T06:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T13:25:02.000Z","uid":21305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"687aef198c9929391262213186007d1033bb230a","tid":607242,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"【台警轟22槍】鸚鵡「QQ」子彈亂飛都冇走 匪徒：去邊都帶佢！<br />\n<br />\n台灣高雄市特勤中隊今開22槍查獲「流動軍火庫」，警方控制現場後發現車上有一隻活鸚鵡，因色彩鮮豔，且未飛離現場或躁動，引發關注。<br />\n<br />\n落網疑犯之一的洪億原對警方表示，鸚鵡名叫「QQ」，品種是吸蜜彩虹鸚鵡，他1年多之前花費6,000多元（新台幣，約1,600港元）買來幼鳥飼養至今，「但不知公母」，因為「QQ」不用關在鳥籠內也不會飛走，所以他都會帶着「QQ」一起外出，「不論做甚麼事，都會帶牠一起！」<br />\n洪男說，這次他要跟朋友一起到南投戒毒，擔心「QQ」在高雄沒人照顧，於是帶着牠一起隨行，沒想到竟然遇到警匪槍戰。<br />\n警方說，洪男與同夥陳羿丞仍在錄取口供，警方目前將鸚鵡「QQ」安置在陳羿丞的車內，「有打開窗戶縫隙，不會讓鸚鵡被悶死！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180327/58000079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F58000079&d=NrUMFqPQK8uRPtOwRQLeh49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5daff60c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F58000079&h=0b4965be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180327/58000079</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295658e7ad6ba81f96db181e52f7c69a4ad16d37","tid":607242,"uid":21305,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180327/large/1522120667_511a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F1522120667_511a.jpg&h=37fd5aa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9898432279c2a9bad2a2f243a42ba6636b622924","tid":607242,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"QQ=700"},{"pid":"c813c57ab00eab693bb9b6cfbfbca92434218da6","tid":607242,"uid":13550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:49:17.000Z","msg":"007=QQ"},{"pid":"e8f9daec90a8d9fd8ae4095d2dd73894dddbd2be","tid":607242,"uid":70258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e7d2a6a1a2424ed0223911bbe18f6615d44ae4","tid":607242,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc8e195ea33c8bd89864b2882716abf28334fed","tid":607242,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"00Q=77"}]}